reviewText: This doctor will get everyone healthy if you just give him a chance.  The diet is healthy and easy to follow. Anyone can do a diet for 10 days. You can see how it works and if it shows promise like everyone else that's tried it so far keep going.  I just started today, can't wait to see how it goes.
The Blood Sugar Solution "QUIZZES & RECIPES"  CD will not play, but the Workshop 1 did  and it was O.K.
